OL,3,CSouth West Water trial to charge less
OL,4,Cin winter and more in summer
OL,6,FA new trial scheme will see some
OL,7,Fpeople charged more for their water in
OL,8,Fthe summer but less in winter.
OL,10,FSouth West Water (SWW) has selected
OL,11,F3,500 households and businesses across
OL,12,FDevon, Cornwall, Bristol and
OL,13,FBournemouth to take part in the two-
OL,14,Fyear project.
OL,16,FThe company said the purpose of the
OL,17,Ftrial is "to find fairer ways to
OL,18,Fcharge customers, while protecting the
OL,19,Fnatural environment."
