OL,3,CSouth West Water trial to charge less
OL,4,Cin winter and more in summer
OL,6,FSWW said it has "carefully considered"
OL,7,Fthe customers who will be on the trial
OL,8,Fand has excluded people on social
OL,9,Ftariffs.
OL,11,FThe customers on the new tariffs will
OL,12,Fbe "supported throughout", the company
OL,13,Fadded.
OL,15,FCustomers on the seasonal tariff will
OL,16,Fbe given lower rates between October
OL,17,Fand March, but will have to pay a
OL,18,Fhigher price for the rest of the year
OL,19,Fduring the summer months.
