OL,3,CSouth West Water trial to charge less
OL,4,Cin winter and more in summer
OL,6,FThose on the summer peak tariff will
OL,7,Fget a lower than normal base price for
OL,8,Fwater during the summer months - that
OL,9,Fincreases once they use a certain
OL,10,Famount.
OL,12,FSWW's Head of Customer Communications
OL,13,FEngagement Dani Twelvetree, said: "We
OL,14,Funderstand that our customers are
OL,15,Flooking for fairer ways to be charged
OL,16,Ffor their water usage.
