OL,6,F"These new tariffs are a direct
OL,7,Fresponse to that feedback, offering
OL,8,Fmore control over bills and
OL,9,Fencouraging year-round water
OL,10,Fefficiency."
OL,12,FThe trial is being supported by
OL,13,Fregulator Ofwat and the Consumer
OL,14,FCouncil for Water (CCW).
